          Does Siah1a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">target group</ENAMEX> I mGluRs for
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">proteolysis</ENAMEX>?
          Siah1a has been shown to be a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">member</ENAMEX> of the ubiquitin
