          was fused to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">C-terminus</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">GFP</ENAMEX> (figure 5A). Figure
          4Aillustrates sample currents from a cell expressing
