          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">33</NUMEX> Â± <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">4%</NUMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">n</ENAMEX> = <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">7</NUMEX>). In <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">cells expressing mGluR5a</ENAMEX> and
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">GFP-Siah1a-CT</ENAMEX>, inhibition was reduced to <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">14 Â± 3</NUMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">n</ENAMEX> = <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">6</NUMEX>; p
          < <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.05</NUMEX>; figure 5B). Therefore, a ubiquitin-deficient
