          The role of Calmodulin
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Calmodulin</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CaM</ENAMEX>), a calcium binding protein
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">intricately</ENAMEX> involved in intracellular signaling,
