          Finally, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CaM</ENAMEX> binding to the mGluRs did not appear to be
          Ca <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX>+-dependent. When results obtained in the presence of
